    "long_instructions": "# Making Sprites\r\n\r\n<div style=\"float:right\">\r\n\r\n![expandable](https://images.code.org/c473902f262d99da7e5a212ec4aa400b-image-1610480180510.png)\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nTo make a sprite, open the **Sprites** category of the toolbox and drag out this block:\r\n\r\n<xml><block type=\"gamelab_makeNewSpriteAnon\"><title name=\"ANIMATION_NAME\">\"face_strawberry_1\"</title></block></xml>\r\n\r\n## Do This\r\n\r\n* Connect a `make new sprite` block under the `when run` block.\r\n* Choose a costume for your sprite.\r\n* Press the \"Run\" button when your code is finished.\r\n\r\n",
